        <div class="descriptionText"><div>
	<p>The chief task of the <em>Ministry of Petroleum and Energy</em> is to develop a coordinated and coherent energy policy. It is an overriding goal to ensure high value creation through the efficient and environmentally-friendly management of the country’s energy resources.</p>
<p>On this page you will find general information and documents relating to energy. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p>
</div></div>
